    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle F(\mathbf {x} _{n+1})=F(\mathbf {x} _{n})+(\mathbf {x} _{n+1}-\mathbf {x} _{n})\cdot \nabla F(\mathbf {x} _{n})+o(||\mathbf {x} _{n+1}-\mathbf {x} _{n}||)\quad \quad (3)}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/58d1e174862af6df429652fd4c0c94723d1c59c2" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:68.383ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle F(\mathbf {x} _{n+1})=F(\mathbf {x} _{n})+(\mathbf {x} _{n+1}-\mathbf {x} _{n})\cdot \nabla F(\mathbf {x} _{n})+o(||\mathbf {x} _{n+1}-\mathbf {x} _{n}||)\quad \quad (3)}"></span></dd></dl></dd></dl>
<p><br />
e substituindo por (1) obtemos (desprezando o termo <a href="/wiki/Infinitesimal" title="Infinitesimal">infinitesimal</a>):
</p>
<dl><dd><dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle F(\mathbf {x} _{n+1})-F(\mathbf {x} _{n})\approx \omega _{n}\mathbf {d} _{n}\cdot \nabla F(\mathbf {x} _{n})\quad \quad (4)}">
