<p>porque
</p>
<dl><dd><dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle (-\nabla F(\mathbf {x} _{n}))\cdot \nabla F(\mathbf {x} _{n})=-||\nabla F(\mathbf {x} _{n})||^{2}&lt;0\quad \quad (6)}">
